%html{:lang => "en"}
  %head
    %meta{:charset => "UTF-8"}
      %title Shopify Sinatra Bootstrap | Login
  %body
    %h1 Login
    %p
    First you have to register this app with a shop to allow access to its private admin data.
    
    %form{:action => "/login/authenticate", :method => "post"}
      %label{:for => "shop"}
        %strong
          The URL of the Shop
          %span.hint (or just the subdomain if it's at myshopify.com)
      %p
        %input{:name => "shop", :type => "text"}
        %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Authenticate"}